Package: a2tools
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Amine Tbaik <tbaik.amine@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 282
Depends: apache2, certbot, curl, dnsutils, jq, libxml2-utils, logrotate, sqlite3, whois
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Description: Apache virtual host, domain, and ACME tooling
 A2Tools provides shell utilities for Apache site management, domain
 registrar automation, ACME certificate issuance via DNS-01 challenges,
 and provider credential management.
 .
 Routine certificate renewals are handled by certbot's own systemd timer
 together with the a2tools deploy hook; a weekly systemd timer prunes
 stale entries from the local domains database.
